---
description: Standards for LLM integration
globs: "**/llm_*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use langchain abstractions for all LLM interactions
- Always include temperature parameter in LLM calls
- Use the strength parameter (0.0 to 1.0) to control model selection
- Implement appropriate error handling and retry logic
- Use appropriate output parsers (StrOutputParser or PydanticOutputParser)
- Support both structured and unstructured output formats
- Always track token usage for cost monitoring
- Support both cloud and local execution modes
